OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784917111
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after police find
OL,4,Ccocaine hidden in plug socket
OL,6,FA drug dealer has been sentenced to
OL,7,Ffour years and six months in prison by
OL,8,FJersey's Royal Court after a drug
OL,9,Ftrafficking operation found cocaine,
OL,10,Fcannabis, and cash believed to be
OL,11,Flinked to a drug supply hidden in his
OL,12,Fhome.
OL,14,FStates of Jersey Police conducted a
OL,15,FMisuse of Drugs Law warrant at the St
OL,16,FHelier home of Robert John Ingram
OL,17,FMoon, 47, on 30 January 2025.
OL,19,FDuring the search, officers found
OL,20,Fsignificant quantities of cocaine,
OL,21,Fcannabis, and drug paraphernalia.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
