FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784917111
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after police find
OL,4,Ccocaine hidden in plug socket
OL,6,FThis included a false plug socket
OL,7,Fconcealing several bags of cocaine.
OL,9,FMoon was convicted of multiple drug-
OL,10,Frelated offences, including being
OL,11,Fconcerned in the supply of Class A, B
OL,12,Fand C controlled drugs, possession
OL,13,Fwith intent to supply cocaine,
OL,14,Fpossession of controlled drugs, and
OL,15,Fpossession of criminal property.
OL,17,FForensic examination linked Moon
OL,18,Fdirectly to the concealment and its
OL,19,Fcontents through fingerprint evidence.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784917111
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after police find
OL,4,Ccocaine hidden in plug socket
OL,6,FOfficers also identified that cocaine
OL,7,Fwas being prepared within the property.
OL,9,FMoon described himself as an
OL,10,F'Accredited Dealer' to customers via
OL,11,Fhis mobile, which was seized during
OL,12,Fthe police operation.
OL,14,FThe mobile also revealed messages,
OL,15,Fvideos, and images promoting the
OL,16,Favailability of controlled drugs, with
OL,17,FMoon providing customers with his
OL,18,Fpricing and what drugs were available.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
