PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784917111
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after police find
OL,4,Ccocaine hidden in plug socket
OL,6,FIn subsequent interviews, Moon claimed
OL,7,Fthat his involvement with drug
OL,8,Ftrafficking was involuntary and a
OL,9,Fresult of duress.
OL,11,FDetective Constable Edward Howgate,
OL,12,FOfficer in the Case, said the
OL,13,Fconviction and subsequent sentence
OL,14,Fdemonstrate a commitment to
OL,15,F"identifying, disrupting and
OL,16,Fprosecuting those who profit from the
OL,17,Fsale of illegal drugs in Jersey".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
