CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784917111
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after police find
OL,4,Ccocaine hidden in plug socket
OL,6,F"This investigation uncovered clear
OL,7,Fevidence of commercial drug dealing,
OL,8,Fincluding the distribution of
OL,9,Fcontrolled drugs, cash, communications
OL,10,Frelating to supply and financial
OL,11,Fevidence consistent with drug
OL,12,Ftrafficking.
OL,14,F"We will continue to target
OL,15,Findividuals involved in the supply of
OL,16,Fcontrolled substances and work to
OL,17,Freduce the harm they cause to our
OL,18,Fcommunity."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
